text: Fettjeåfallet Fettjeåfallet is a waterfall located just west of Klövsjö in Fettjeån (Fättjeån), Jämtland, Sweden. It has a height of about . It is a popular destination of hikers in the summer and for ice climbing in the winter. ==References== Category:Waterfalls of Sweden Category:Geography of Jämtland County
